A unique tetranuclear Cu(II)-based 2D aggregate containing 26-membered Cu(II)ade 
macrocycles, [Cu(4)(DMF)(6)(mu(4)-ade)(2)(mu(2)-Cl)(2)Cl(4)](n) (1; Hade = 
